  "title": "Material Planner (Electronics Mfg/ Loyang Area) Entry level are welcome",
  "description": "<ul><li>Generated MRP and advise Purchasing on the procurement of raw materials</li><li>Coordinate with respective sections to ensure raw materials on-time schedule</li><li>Monitor and coordinate with production and Store to ensure smooth supply of raw materials</li><li>Update of materials arrival date in the daily sales order listing</li><li>Daily input review to ensure material availability for production</li><li>Review, analyze forecast accuracy, consumption trends and production capacity</li><li>Materials forecast orientation with Purchasing/Supplier base on Sales forecast</li><li>Work closely with Sales, Purchasing and Warehouse to update the forecast and ensure on-time ordering, receipt, delivery of raw materials</li><li>Identify, negotiate, and resolve any conflict with different departments related to material availability, Capacity, and order fulfilment</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in manufacturing/supply chain management/engineering or any related fields</li><li>Knowledge in MRP system preferred</li><li>Basic inventory management and warehouse management</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills with ability to interact with various stakeholders</li><li>Adaptable and able to perform effectively in a fast-paced environment with changing priorities</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Excel and other office applications</li><li>Entry level are welcome as training will be provided. </li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>5 days work week</strong></p><p><strong>Electronics Engineering</strong></p><p><strong>Loyang Area</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Interested Applicants, kindly email your detailed resume to <strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>License No: 06C3745</p><p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
